  <description><![CDATA[<p>We’re delighted to offer the superior family-run Hotel Sun Valley, which enjoys a panoramic sunny position in the centre of the village, just 2 minutes' walk (150m) from the Ciampinoi gondola. Providing a most comfortable base for walkers, the hotel’s excellent cuisine, smart Alpine style interiors and particularly attractive spa centre with indoor pool are all on hand to offer total relaxation and rejuvenation to both tired legs and minds.</p>]]></description>
